# KPPDF integration

- Base URL: `KPPDF_API_URL` = `http://localhost:3000/api/v1`
- Products: `GET /directories/products?page=&limit=`
- Categories: `GET /directories/categories?page=&limit=`
- Login: `POST /auth/login` body `{ username, password }` — tokens from Set-Cookie
- Refresh: `POST /auth/refresh` with refresh cookie/token on 401
- Pagination response: `{ success, data: T[], total, page, limit, totalPages }`
- Permission codes (`office.products.view`) ≠ URL paths

Shared types must match [action-plan INewsItem](../../docs/plans/ai-analyst-action-plan.md).
